{"article_id":"8TvH1VThkW6ECz82","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"No agreement came out of a meeting between U.S. congressional leaders and President Donald Trump on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"to end a partial government shutdown now in its 12th day","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"as the president stuck to his demand for $ 5 billion in border wall funding","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"fiercely opposed by Democrats .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Congressional leaders are expected to return to the White House on Friday","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"to resume talks ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"signaling","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"the shutdown will likely stretch into the weekend .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"The White House convened the meeting","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"to try to convince Democrats","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"that funding a wall on the southern border with Mexico was a pressing security need .","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"Instead , Democratic leaders cut off Homeland Security Secretary Kirstjen Neilsen ' s presentation","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"and tried to no avail to press Trump to accept their offer .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"\" It just was not a credible presentation , \"","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Senator Dick Durbin said of the briefing .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"He added","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that Senate Minority Leader Chuck Schumer and Nancy Pelosi ,","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"who is expected to be elected House speaker on Thursday ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"insisted","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"the conversation focus instead on the shutdown .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Pelosi said","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"the House would proceed with plans","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"to hold votes on Thursday ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"when they formally take control of the chamber from Trump ' s fellow Republicans ,","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"on legislation","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that would end the shutdown","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"without providing the wall money","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"sought by Trump .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"\" We ' re asking the president to open up government , \"","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"Pelosi told reporters outside the White House after the meeting .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"But Senate Majority Leader Mitch McConnell said afterward on the Senate floor","depth":7},{"id":32,"text":"that the chamber would not vote on the legislation ,","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"calling it a \" political sideshow \" and \" total nonstarter . \"","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"Democrats say","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"they want to fund most of the government through September ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"but allow for another month","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"to negotiate wall funding","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"by only partially funding the Department of Homeland Security ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"which is responsible for the wall .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Schumer said","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"Trump conceded","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"that Republicans would lose leverage","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"if they allowed the rest of the government to be funded .","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"\" We asked him to give us one good reason ...","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"why you should continue your shutdown of the eight Cabinet departments","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"while we are debating our differences on homeland security .","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"He could not give a good answer , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Schumer told reporters after the meeting .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"In a tweet on Wednesday evening , Trump called the meeting \" important \"","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"and said","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"he would continue talks with Democrats","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"\" to pass a bill","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"that secures our borders ,","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"supports the agents and officers on the ground ,","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"and keeps America Safe . \"","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump leads a Cabinet meeting on day 12 of the partial U.S. government shutdown at the White House in Washington , U.S. , January 2 , 2019 .","depth":4},{"id":57,"text":"/Jim Young","depth":4},{"id":58,"text":"Trump ' s demand for $ 5 billion in funding for a wall along the U.S.-Mexico border triggered the shutdown","depth":6},{"id":59,"text":"affecting about a quarter of the federal government and 800,000 federal workers .","depth":6},{"id":60,"text":"Before meeting with lawmakers ,","depth":8},{"id":61,"text":"Trump said","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"the shutdown would last for \" as long","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"as it takes \"","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"as he pushes for wall money as part of any legislation","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"to reopen agencies","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"shuttered","depth":13},{"id":67,"text":"when their funding lapsed on Dec. 22 .","depth":13},{"id":68,"text":"\" It could be a long time , \"","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Trump told reporters on Wednesday during a Cabinet meeting ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"\" or it could be quickly . \"","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"\" We know","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"that we have a challenge along the border , \"","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"said Kevin McCarthy , the top House Republican .","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"\" We want to solve that issue .","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"We want to make sure","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"we open this government up .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"And I think","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"at the end of the day , the president ,","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"listening to him ,","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"he wants to solve this as well . \"","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Pelosi noted","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"that the legislation","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"being presented in the House","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"had previously won backing in the Senate ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"which will remain in Republican hands in the new 2019-2020 Congress","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"that convenes on Thursday .","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"But McConnell said previously","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"that Senate Republicans would not approve a spending measure","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"Trump does not support .","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"Trump made the border wall a key part of his presidential campaign .","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Before meeting with the Democrats ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"Trump called the border a \" sieve , \"","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"rebutted Pelosi ' s complaint","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"that a wall was immoral ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"provided an estimate of the U.S. illegal immigrant population far higher than the figures","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"most experts cite","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"and made disputed comments about progress","depth":13},{"id":98,"text":"toward building a wall .","depth":13},{"id":99,"text":"The visit by Pelosi and Schumer was their first to the White House since their sharp exchange with Trump in the Oval Office on Dec. 11","depth":8},{"id":100,"text":"during which the president told them","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"he would be \" proud to shut down the government for border security . \"","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"The $ 5 billion","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"Trump is seeking","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"would cover only a portion of the money","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"needed for a border wall , a project","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"estimated to cost about $ 23 billion .","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"Trump had said","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Mexico would pay for the wall ,","depth":8},{"id":109,"text":"but Mexico has refused .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":219,"left":0,"right":218,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},